optional_services:
The following optional service can be added to the standard services as part of this service:
Internet Access
The following additional services will be delivered as part of this additional service:
Maintain Internet Access Traffic Profile within Global Secure Access;
Maintain Internet Access Features like:
Security Profile
Web content Filtering Policies
Provide Dashboard of the Internet Access including the following information:
Alerts and Notifications (last 24 hours);
Traffic Insights for Internet Access;
Additional Technical L2/L3 incident handling for Entra Internet Access Platform
Private Access
The following additional services will be delivered as part of this additional service:
Maintain Private Access Features like:
Quick Access with or without Private DNS;
Application Discovery
Enterprise Applications
Conditional Access support for applications within Private Access
Maintain Private Access Traffic Profile within Global Secure Access
Maintain on Private Access Connectors;
Updating the connectors with at least n-1 version of the connector software;
High availability of the connector groups (at least 2 connectors per group);
Provide Dashboard of the Private Access including the following information:
Alerts and Notifications (last 24 hours);
Connector Status
Traffic Insights Private Access;

differentiators:
