Maintain the Microsoft 365 Traffic Profile within Global Secure Access;
Maintain and keep Global Secure Access clients up to date;
Only when not integrated in the core of the corresponding operating system;
Provide Dashboard of the Global Secure Access Platform including the following information:
Alerts and Notifications (last 24 hours);
Client Activity Status
Traffic Insights;
Technical L2/L3 incident handling for Global Secure Access Platform and the Microsoft 365 traffic profile & Private Access
